1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=Happiness Awaits in a Life with Love=

4
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:51,470
Why did you tell her not to hurt me?

5
00:00:52,150 --> 00:00:53,470
You've spent your whole life

6
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:56,150
protecting Zhaoli.

7
00:00:56,161 --> 00:00:58,203
Yet you two are destined
to turn against each other

8
00:00:58,214 --> 00:00:59,189
due to misunderstandings.

9
00:01:00,670 --> 00:01:02,750
That is the fate between you and her.

10
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,800
Ying Du,

11
00:01:04,070 --> 00:01:05,200
I don't want your future

12
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,510
to be filled with pain like mine.

13
00:01:07,350 --> 00:01:08,480
How do you know that?

14
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,790
You're Zhaoli from another world.

15
00:01:15,150 --> 00:01:15,990
Yes.

16
00:01:18,590 --> 00:01:19,590
(Seeing her cry,)

17
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,120
(my heart aches so much.)

18
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:22,970
Ying Du,

19
00:01:23,070 --> 00:01:24,870
no matter what, I will change this fate.

20
00:01:25,146 --> 00:01:26,710
Before you see me again, you must not...

21
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:27,560
What is it?

22
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,579
You must not fall for me.

23
00:01:28,590 --> 00:01:30,040
It will drag you into endless sorrow.

24
00:01:30,770 --> 00:01:31,620
Zhaoli.

25
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,680
Your mother's passing

26
00:01:32,691 --> 00:01:33,640
was never my intention.

27
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:35,000
Enough, Ying Du.

28
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,120
You have no right to speak of my mother.

29
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,870
She died because of you.

30
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:39,760
Zhaoli!

31
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:43,680
You claim to protect me,

32
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:46,040
but it's just guilt over my mother.

33
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,400
Every bit of care and kindness
you've shown me

34
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:51,920
was part of a deal with her.

35
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,480
Everything you've done

36
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:57,430
was only to gain her power.

37
00:01:57,950 --> 00:02:00,000
You're not worthy to be my brother.

38
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,560
The day I learned my mother

39
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,430
died because of you,

40
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:07,000
I longed to kill you with my own hands

41
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,680
to avenge my mother's suffering.

42
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,400
Zhaoli, don't!

43
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:11,550
Please, no!

44
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,640
Don't!

45
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:23,430
Ying Du.

46
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:27,710
(Is it you who has returned?)

47
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,960
Could this be

48
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,710
the fate between Ying Du and me?

49
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,190
Why?

50
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:47,080
Why can't I escape this fate?

51
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,910
I cannot accept this.

52
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,190
I refuse to accept it!

53
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,870
What was meant to come

54
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:53,910
has come at last.

55
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,080
What is going on?

56
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,120
Ying Du!

57
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:10,590
Ying Du, no!

58
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:16,190
No, Ying Du!

59
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,960
Ying Du.

60
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,360
Ying Du.

61
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:26,310
Ying Du, why would you do this?

62
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:27,800
At last,

63
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,310
I have fulfilled my mission.

64
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,680
Ying Du,

65
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:34,960
what exactly is your mission?

66
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:40,470
Goddess,

67
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,280
what is the calamity

68
00:03:44,310 --> 00:03:45,400
you spoke of?

69
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:50,000
Goddesses bear immense power

70
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,800
yet are bound by fate.

71
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,030
We must never fall in love.

72
00:03:55,190 --> 00:03:57,910
Or we shall face punishment.

73
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,400
But I could not restrain my heart,

74
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,840
and I fell for a mortal man.

75
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:05,150
I even bore him my daughter.

76
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,120
Yet fate

77
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,750
was so cruel.

78
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,710
It took the life of the man I loved

79
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,840
and placed the punishment

80
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,590
upon my daughter.

81
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,750
The punishment?

82
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,880
Yes.

83
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:21,040
Fate has punished her

84
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:22,190
with a life without love.

85
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,810
It cast her into the abyss of hatred,

86
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,560
with nothing left to hope for.

87
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,870
Her power has been sealed.

88
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:31,720
I only wish she could live
as an ordinary soul

89
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,430
following her heart.

90
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:35,070
But one day,

91
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:36,480
her power will awaken.

92
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,270
The punishment will return.

93
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:40,600
By then, I hope you'll keep your word

94
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,190
and take that punishment in her place.

95
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,680
If you choose not to,

96
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,390
I will understand.

97
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,310
If sacrificing me alone

98
00:04:51,750 --> 00:04:53,240
can save countless lives,

99
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,190
why would I refuse?

100
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,310
As her mother,

101
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,680
I will be forever grateful

102
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,360
to you.

103
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:07,790
Ying Du.

104
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,030
Ying Du.

105
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,230
So,

106
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:13,480
all this was fate's punishment.

107
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,920
And Ying Du...

108
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:18,120
He bore the punishment for me.

109
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,410
Ying Du,

110
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:21,160
you kept this from me for so many years.

111
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:24,870
Why didn't you tell me?

112
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,630
Fate.

113
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:33,560
I never imagined

114
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:35,310
that fate would take away

115
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,070
my mother's right to love.

116
00:05:38,390 --> 00:05:40,240
Nor did I expect my existence

117
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:42,720
to be fate's punishment.

118
00:05:42,870 --> 00:05:45,950
Yet you endured all this pain for me.

119
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,560
Fate...

120
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,000
Fate.

121
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,200
Zhaoli,

122
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,950
what are you trying to do?

123
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:58,870
Why must the laws of all things

124
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,560
be bound by fate's will?

125
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,560
- Zhaoli.
- I refuse to obey.

126
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,390
I choose to stand against fate!

127
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,220
Don't, Zhaoli!

128
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:10,170
Zhaoli!

129
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,640
Zhaoli!

130
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:14,710
Zhaoli!

131
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:15,720
Zhaoli!

132
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,520
Zhaoli!

133
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,110
No.

134
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,240
I won't let destiny repeat itself.

135
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,390
I must bring her back.

136
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,040
I must save Zhaoli.

137
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,510
What was meant to come

138
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:49,560
has come at last.

139
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,390
It's that lady.

140
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:11,040
She saved us.

141
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:20,990
Du,

142
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,000
are you all right?

143
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,240
Fate is written by the heavens.

144
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:29,800
It is the destiny
of your Goddess lineage.

145
00:07:30,630 --> 00:07:33,360
Why must you walk toward death?

146
00:07:38,630 --> 00:07:40,310
This so‑called destiny you speak of

147
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,430
is utterly absurd.

148
00:07:42,476 --> 00:07:43,720
My mother refused to bow to it,

149
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,950
and I refuse even more.

150
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:49,830
What sin is there in loving someone?

151
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,040
My mother did no wrong,

152
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:54,710
and Ying Du

153
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,430
was even more undeserving of such pain.

154
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,920
Desire breeds chaos.

155
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:03,040
The Goddess's power is immense,

156
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:05,830
so she should never have felt affection.

157
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,800
Without small affections,

158
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,430
how could there be great love?

159
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,120
My mother exhausted herself for me;

160
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,360
Ying Du suffered endlessly
because of me.

161
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,510
Fate,

162
00:08:16,830 --> 00:08:17,750
if you insist

163
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,720
on passing down this punishment,

164
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,120
let me bear it instead.

165
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,550
I wish only for Ying Du

166
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:35,270
to enjoy peace and joy forever,

167
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:39,030
with all his desires fulfilled,

168
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,270
a life filled with love,

169
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,510
and happiness within reach.

170
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,150
You've endured heaven's punishment.

171
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,910
The cycle of cause and effect is gone.

172
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,790
From this moment on,

173
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,480
there will be no more Goddess
in this world.

174
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:55,200
Your destiny

175
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,390
is yours to decide.

176
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:03,940
(Winter, Year 5 of Yuanqi)

177
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:25,910
I'm still alive.

178
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:30,630
I am back.

179
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:36,910
Ying Du stayed in the Rongxi Era.

180
00:10:08,010 --> 00:10:11,860
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

181
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:14,280
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

182
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:18,300
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

183
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,600
A life filled with love

184
00:10:19,790 --> 00:10:20,870
and happiness within reach.

185
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:21,960
Zhaoli,

186
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,910
you've grown better at making wishes.

187
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:27,920
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

188
00:10:28,070 --> 00:10:33,880
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

189
00:10:34,540 --> 00:10:39,400
♪One more glance may let love♪

190
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:41,020
♪Stand still♪

191
