♪Hard to tell them apart♪

196
00:11:04,130 --> 00:11:09,420
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

197
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:13,120
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

198
00:11:13,470 --> 00:11:15,820
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

199
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:19,860
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

200
